Somme indications for the execution of the chapter 16 examples
--------------------------------------------------------------

This chapter proposed a number of examples concerning the basic
TBB task scheduler. Besides the examples discussed in the book,
there are a few other additional examples incorporated here, that
may be useful.

To compile all book examples      :  make all
To run all book examples          :  make runall

To compile all additional examples  :  make allx
To run all additional examples      :  make runallx

The makefile in this directory has a clear separation of the book
and additional examples. The source files explain the example meaning
and purpose.
